{
  "stem": "2539.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Except my mother sent me-- the following day, after I left them, somebody else was joining.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She sent me a piece of bread and some-- I don't know what was there-- a piece of bread and maybe a tomato.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't remember what else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She sent me from the ghetto-- the sick woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had nothing themselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she sent me-- because she thought I might be starving there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was the next day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because two days later, they were all killed Anyway, the point is that we hid there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, there was-- the ghetto were finished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They-- they eradicated the whole ghetto between the 22nd of August and the 25th or 26th of August.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everyone was killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I heard that that the trucks came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were loaded on the trucks, taken to a small place three kilometers out of the city-- out of the town, in a little forest, where originally, a few men went to dig the grave.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they shot them in-- in-- right into the grave.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then they shot everybody from Lutsk right-- you know, on the-- they're bringing them by trucks, shooting them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were falling into the graves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the next truck came, and-- well, I visited this place last year.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think on the grave it states-- I-- I think the figure given on the grave is 27,000-- that 27,000 people lie in this grave.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you should see the size of it-- like this table-- no, bigger-- like this-- this-- well--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Small-- 27,000 people in one grave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that-- that happened in August-- August, 1942.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the thing that really makes me very angry is when people now don't mention the eradication of the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
